text: Philippa Cross (born 7 July 1966) is a British rower. She competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. Cross also represented Durham University Women's Boat Club. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:British female rowers Category:Durham University Boat Club rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Great Britain Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Banbury
